(- ring of vertices at roof height) Tj T*
(- triangle fan from tip to ring) Tj T*
(- indices connect the mesh) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Mention your parameters:) Tj T*
(- segment count) Tj T*
(- min/max radius) Tj T*
(- min/max tip height) Tj T*
(- roof width/depth) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Random Placement) Tj T*
(Explain:) Tj T*
(- random \(x, z\) positions are sampled inside the roof dimensions) Tj T*
(- positions are rejected if too close to existing icicles) Tj T*
(- this prevents heavy overlap) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Normals and Lighting) Tj T*
(Explain:) Tj T*
(- normals are needed for lighting) Tj T*
(- diffuse lighting uses dot product between normal and light direction) Tj T*
(- specular/rim/alpha if currently in your shader) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Example phrasing:) Tj T*
(The fragment shader uses the interpolated normal to calculate how much each surface faces the) Tj T*
(light. This makes the icicles appear three-dimensional instead of flat.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Background Texture) Tj T*
(Explain:) Tj T*
(- iceCave.jpg is rendered as a fullscreen quad) Tj T*
(- it uses a separate shader) Tj T*
(- depth testing is disabled while drawing the background) Tj T*
(- depth testing is enabled again before drawing icicles) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5. Settings) Tj T*
(===========) Tj T*
(List important constants:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Icicle count: 6000) Tj T*
(Segments per icicle: 24) Tj T*
(Radius range: 0.05 to 0.20) Tj T*
(Tip height range: -0.8 to -0.1) Tj T*
(Roof size: 7 x 7) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Also mention controls:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(W/S: camera movement) Tj T*
(1/2: wireframe/fill mode) Tj T*
(ESC: close window) Tj T*
() Tj T*
